    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I found that the `help()` function is provided by the python REPL instead of ipython; which calls `pydoc.help`, a predefined instance of class `pydoc.Helper`, which is callable. \r\n\r\nTo disable the pager, just do the following\r\n\r\n    import pydoc, sys\r\n    pydoc.help = pydoc.Helper(output=sys.stdout)\r\n\r\nSo this issue can be closed now."
  },
